      "message": "Not necessarily, technically, it needs a trailing backslash (or slash) to be absolute.\n\nMaybe one solution would be to do like Chromium does, i.e. implement a Path class that encapsulates everything a path needs to be. See https://github.com/adobe/chromium/blob/master/base/file_path.h for more information.",
